Title: KitchenAid — Since 1919
Author: wavelet-director

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - MORNING

Soft dough drops into the polished steel bowl of a KitchenAid Artisan stand mixer in empire red. Close-up, slow-motion impact.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - MORNING

A hand pulls the chrome lever and tilts the mixer head down. The latch clicks home with a precise mechanical thunk.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - MORNING

Macro: the spiral dough hook rotates slowly, dough folding over itself, catching shape against the bowl wall.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - MORNING

Wide reveal: the empire-red Artisan sits centered on a marble counter. Warm window light spills from camera-left across the metal surface.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - MORNING

Hands shape proofed dough on a flour-dusted board, the mixer visible soft in the background.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN OVEN - MORNING

A finished crusty loaf is pulled from the oven on a cast-iron tray, steam rising in the warm light.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - MORNING

A clean white card with the KitchenAid wordmark holds the frame.

FADE OUT.
